This is a beta release of vcode.  It works on MIPS, SPARC, and Alpha
architectures.  A (manually maintained) mailing list to discuss vcode
has been setup: email engler@lcs.mit.edu to get on it.

To build vcode type
	`perl install'

Useful information will be printed during the installation.  

Contents:
	./vcode-src contains the vcode library and header files
	./examples contains a number of vcode examples
	./tests contain some regression tests.
	./doc contains a vcode tutorial and the original pldi paper
